# Privacy Policy

## No Personal Data Collection

GTFKD is committed to protecting the privacy of our users.

We do not collect,
store, or sell any personal data.

Cloudflare may collect data such as IP addresses,
User-Agents, and behaviors as part of its operational requirements.

This data
collection is purely for the purpose of maintaining network security and
operational integrity.

Please be aware that Cloudflare's data collection is governed by their own
privacy policy, which we recommend you review to understand their practices.
